Name: MedComCoreInterpretationCodes
Title: MedComCoreInterpretationCodes
Description: CodeSystem with code for interpretation of an observation

Name: MedComObservationCodes
Title: MedComObservationCodes
Description: CodeSystem with observations codes used in HomeCareObservation

Name: ObservationInterpretation
Title: ObservationInterpretation
Description: One or more codes providing a rough qualitative interpretation of the observation, such as "normal" / "abnormal", "low" / "high", "better" / "worse", "resistant" / "susceptible", "expected" / "not expected". The value set is intended to be for ANY use where coded representation of an interpretation is needed.

Name: NPU
Title: DK NPU Subset
Description: DK NPU Subsetted code system used in DK Core. The full version of NPU can be found at http://labterm.dk
